&lt;li&gt;Provide feedback on team members&#39; output, encouraging skills development within the team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Portfolio Managers and Decision Scientists to understand the real world problems we’re trying to solve&lt;/li&gt;
